# URL Shortener

A simple **URL shortener** built with **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**.  
Generate short URLs, track visits, and view analytics for each short URL.

---

## Features

- Generate short URLs from long URLs
- Redirect to original URL via short URL
- Track visits with timestamps
- View analytics (total clicks and visit history)

---

## Technologies Used

- Node.js & Express
- MongoDB & Mongoose
- shortid (for generating unique short IDs)
- nodemon (for development)
